ng\",\n    \"priority\": \"high\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"content\": \"Run bun run build to verify everything compiles\",\n    \"status\": \"pending\",\n    \"priority\": \"high\"\n  }\n]","title":"3 todos","metadata":{"todos":[{"content":"Analyze launcher.ts: Are agents spawned with detached:true and unref()? Document findings.","status":"completed","priority":"high"},{"content":"Analyze monitor.ts: Does ProcessMonitor.stop()/killAll() kill child processes? Document findings.","status":"completed","priority":"high"},{"content":"Analyze tui.ts: Does screen.destroy() affect agent processes? Document findings.","status":"completed","priority":"high"},{"content":"Verify existing audit documentation is complete and accurate in all key files","status":"in_progress","priority":"high"},{"content":"Add any missing documentation or fix any gaps in the audit annotations","status":"pending","priority":"high"},{"content":"Run bun run build to verify everything compiles","status":"pending","priority":"high"}],"truncated":false},"time":{"start":1773483394596,"end":1773483394597}}}}
